Highlights.php:366 getFullTextFields()
Mapped fields are 'mapped' to $fields_by_datasource incorrectly. Beginning with an empty index (normal fields: ['entity:node']. Additionally, multiple mapped_field fields on the index will overwrite each other in the array build - Gotcha! This results in a malformed data-array which is passed to extractItemValues()

FieldsHelper.php:222 (extractItemValues()) because of malformed $required_properties passed from getFullTextFields(), the for-loop will return incorrectly mapped data if more than one mapped-field is indexed as fulltext in search-api index! (Gotcha 2). A workaround is to only use one full-text mapped-field in search-api and in the view!

Das Ergebnis-Excerpt ist eine Property von search_api/Item/Item.php. Das Excerpt wird von Highlight.php gesetzt, und zwar aus der Suchphrase + Fulltext-Suchfelder (sehe addExcerpts() in Highlight.php:297 bzw. setExcerpt() in Item.php:377). Wenn wir Highlighting auf unserem Full-Text-Felder aktivieren, ist die RÃ¼ckgabe das gleiche 


