Disable language facet fields for following types b/c they have no standard language field - they are set to default (English) and cant not be changed - not translated:

event
publication
job_offer
press

These can be changed and are translated:

landingpage
knowledge_article *But! language selector disabled - didn't change.
news
press_release
textpage


These can be changed and are NOT translated:
person *But! language selector disabled - didn't change.
program

